36
00:08:25,764 --> 00:08:26,663
Our Economics teacher?

37
00:08:27,034 --> 00:08:29,023
Yes, sir. Our Economics teacher

38
00:08:29,764 --> 00:08:30,663
No man!

39
00:08:31,964 --> 00:08:35,163
Ya man. I know Miss. Kashyap
better than you

40
00:08:38,404 --> 00:08:38,893
Tuitions...

41
00:08:40,814 --> 00:08:41,603
