in Poona?

58
00:11:10,664 --> 00:11:14,253
Ya. It's a very nice.
You must come there sometime

59
00:11:14,994 --> 00:11:15,593
Definitely man

60
00:11:16,564 --> 00:11:18,123
Are you just saying that or
do you really intend on coming?

61
00:11:19,534 --> 00:11:23,163
I intend on doing a lot of things
...like getting married

62
00:11:35,954 --> 00:11:38,783
