186
00:25:20,144 --> 00:25:23,913
Just decide, Sameer. You can
either be with Akash or me!

187
00:25:30,724 --> 00:25:31,283
I am thinking...

188
00:25:32,124 --> 00:25:34,783
You need time to think
if you want to be with me!

189
00:25:38,434 --> 00:25:40,193
Okay. So you want some time?

190
00:25:40,504 --> 00:25:40,963
No!

191
00:25:44,104 --> 00:25:46,833
I'm going out with friends.
I'll be back by 2.00

192
00:25:47,674 --> 00:25:52,073
If I don't hear from you before that,
I'll know what your answer is

193
00:25:56,854 --> 00:25:59,013
Don't you think you are
over-reacting?

194
00:26:01,524 --> 00:26:02,013
No

195
00:26:03,154 --> 00:26:08,613
You've never seen me over-react.
If I do... then God help you!!

196
00:26:31,214 --> 00:26:31,773
What are you doing!

197
00:26:32,684 --> 00:26:37,213
Your bruise has turned a strange colour.
Have you seen it, Sid?

198
00:26:37,894 --> 00:26:39,483
I'm glad you like it!
Do you want one?

199
00:26:40,024 --> 00:26:43,623
Hey! Don't get that anger out on me man

200
00:26:43,934 --> 00:26:45,723
Did I ask you to speak to Shalini?

201
00:26:45,934 --> 00:26:50,993
No. But you could've at least helped me.
You just sat there!

202
00:26:51,534 --> 00:26:55,103
Such a true friend! I think I'd be
better off befriending Rohit

203
00:26:55,214 --> 00:26:56,473
I'd at least get some protection!

204
00:26:59,284 --> 00:27:01,473
May God bless your unity. I'm off.

205
00:27:02,014 --> 00:27:04,143
Where to? -Home.

206
00:27:04,654 --> 00:27:06,383
