Right, Sameer?

207
00:27:06,654 --> 00:27:08,813
Ya, man, chill. It's only
1'O' clock

208
00:27:10,424 --> 00:27:12,583
In which country?
It's nearly 4 here!

209
00:27:31,214 --> 00:27:32,543
I forgot to call Priya!

210
00:27:36,484 --> 00:27:37,783
Why are you so scared of Priya?

211
00:27:38,154 --> 00:27:39,143
I'm not scared of her

212
00:27:40,084 --> 00:27:42,853
I don't want to hurt her
or lose her

213
00:27:43,524 --> 00:27:46,923
Sameer, I can't understand
how you tolerate her

214
00:27:47,294 --> 00:27:48,783
She seems more a boss
than a girlfriend!

215
00:27:50,064 --> 00:27:53,933
Akash, I'm asking for help,
not your expert comments

216
00:27:54,134 --> 00:27:54,763
What should I do?

217
00:27:56,074 --> 00:27:56,793
What do you think?

218
00:27:57,674 --> 00:28:00,263
