551
01:09:56,663 --> 01:09:58,332
Ya, to Akash's... Why?

552
01:10:02,843 --> 01:10:03,632
I'll be back

553
01:10:16,953 --> 01:10:17,972
Mom! What's the matter?

554
01:10:18,223 --> 01:10:20,912
The fact is, Nareshji's daughter
Pooja is coming here

555
01:10:21,863 --> 01:10:25,162
And we want the two of you to...

556
01:10:27,193 --> 01:10:27,992
What! Fixing my marriage...!

557
01:10:30,033 --> 01:10:31,832
An arranged marriage!
No, Mom. Not for me

558
01:10:32,033 --> 01:10:35,162
Why not? Your Daddy and I had
an arranged marriage

559
01:10:36,203 --> 01:10:40,162
Listen to me. We are not forcing
you to get married

560
01:10:40,373 --> 01:10:42,002
We have known them for years

561
01:10:42,213 --> 01:10:44,512
And we thought we'd turn friendship
into a marriage alliance

562
01:10:45,883 --> 01:10:48,352
You don't lose anything by
meeting Pooja, do you?

563
01:10:51,023 --> 01:10:54,722
Okay. But you know my answer.
And that's NO!

564
01:11:00,863 --> 01:11:01,692
Who is it, Sameer?

565
01:11:24,493 --> 01:11:26,852
Er... Sameer, we have something
important to discuss

566
01:11:29,393 --> 01:11:30,722
Nareshji, is that all right?

567
01:11:32,733 --> 01:11:35,752
Anyway, they'll get bored
sitting with us oldies

568
01:11:59,453 --> 01:12:00,922
Are they your friends?

569
01:12:01,563 --> 01:12:02,022
Please sit down

570
01:12:07,293 --> 01:12:09,422
This is Akash and this is Sid

571
01:12:10,733 --> 01:12:12,102
Seems like a deep friendship

572
01:12:12,433 --> 01:12:15,272
Either the friendship is deep
or it's a 3-D photograph

573
01:12:33,353 --> 01:12:37,622
Pooja, you do know why
you're here, don't you?

574
01:12:38,663 --> 01:12:41,392
Yes. Mom and Dad told me

575
01:12:44,973 --> 01:12:46,962
Look, honestly speaking...

576
01:12:47,173 --> 01:12:50,902
When Mom told me about this...
I felt it wasn't right at first...

577
01:12:51,513 --> 01:12:55,812
...but now... I'm so happy you said no to
this arranged marriage bullshit!

578
01:13:02,183 --> 01:13:04,312
I think marriages shouldn't be
made like this

579
01:13:04,523 --> 01:13:07,322
It's so important to love somebody
to get married

580
01:13:08,023 --> 01:13:08,782
What do you think?

581
01:13:09,023 --> 01:13:10,152
Yes, absolutely

582
01:13:13,033 --> 01:13:13,992
Why? Are you in love with
someone?

583
01:13:27,043 --> 01:13:28,472
There is this guy in my life

584
01:13:28,883 --> 01:13:31,572
But I guess I don't love him
enough so far to marry him

585
01:13:32,713 --> 01:13:34,112
I pretty much feel the same...

586
01:13:35,753 --> 01:13:37,412
...but not about the guy in your life!

587
01:13:43,723 --> 01:13:44,522
And then?

588
01:13:45,533 --> 01:13:47,362
Then what!
She went home

589
01:13:51,133 --> 01:13:51,692
It's a problem man

590
01:14:01,543 --> 01:14:04,202
Please don't tell me you've
fallen for her after all this!

591
01:14:08,423 --> 01:14:08,882
Look, Sameer...

592
01:14:09,423 --> 01:14:11,382
I have no doubt whatsoever
you have fallen in love with her

593
01:14:11,923 --> 01:14:14,052
But I'm equally sure that after
3 months...

594
01:14:14,253 --> 01:14:15,412
...you'll be in love with some other
girl

595
01:14:16,193 --> 01:14:16,882
No, Akash

596
01:14:19,433 --> 01:14:22,552
I always thought I knew
what love was

597
01:14:22,763 --> 01:14:24,592
I realized today that I was
completely wrong

598
01:14:25,473 --> 01:14:25,902
Is that so!

599
01:14:27,373 --> 01:14:30,232
Akash, when Pooja told me about
that guy in her life...

600
01:14:30,443 --> 01:14:33,802
For the first time I thought about
all those girls in my life...

601
01:14:34,113 --> 01:14:35,572
I was attracted to all of them...

602
01:14:36,013 --> 01:14:38,032
But I was wrong to think
the attraction was love

603
01:14:40,283 --> 01:14:42,082
And now you love Pooja?

604
01:14:42,283 --> 01:14:46,722
Yes. That's it!
I love Pooja

605
01:14:47,793 --> 01:14:49,422
Then tell her

606
01:14:51,933 --> 01:14:54,692
Take my advice. Don't say
anything to anyone

607
01:14:55,633 --> 01:14:56,602
There's no trusting you

608
01:14:56,803 --> 01:14:58,262
Today it's Pooja,
tomorrow it'll be some Ahuja!

609
